OL,3,CMan jailed after throwing acid in a
OL,4,Cteenager's face
OL,6,FA man who launched an "utterly vile"
OL,7,Fattack on teenage boy by throwing acid
OL,8,Fin his face has been jailed for more
OL,9,Fthan eight years.
OL,11,FGilson Martins, 23, of Ashton Street
OL,12,Fin Rochdale, Greater Manchester,
OL,13,Fplanned the attack, producing the acid
OL,14,Fhimself and demonstrating its effects
OL,15,Fby pouring it on paper.
OL,17,FAn accomplice rang the 16-year-old
OL,18,Fvictim to meet him at an address in
OL,19,Fthe Woodley area of Stockport on 24
OL,20,FMarch 2024.
