OL,3,CMan jailed after throwing acid in a
OL,4,Cteenager's face
OL,6,FShortly before 10pm Martins confronted
OL,7,Fhis victim and when a fight broke out
OL,8,Fhe produced a bottle and threw the
OL,9,Facid in the boy's face. He then fled
OL,10,Fthe scene.
OL,12,FEmergency services were called to
OL,13,Ftreat the injured youngster, with
OL,14,Ftests confirming a corrosive substance
OL,15,Fhad been used.
OL,17,FThe boy was taken to hospital with
OL,18,Fserious injuries and was transferred
OL,19,Fto a specialist burns unit for
OL,20,Fintensive treatment.
