OL,3,CMan jailed after throwing acid in a
OL,4,Cteenager's face
OL,6,FMartins attempted to silence a witness
OL,7,Fwho had spoken to police, kicking in
OL,8,Fthe man's back door and threatening to
OL,9,Fstab him, throw acid on him and carve
OL,10,Fhis name into him.
OL,12,FMartins was arrested by armed police
OL,13,Fdays later and was in possession of
OL,14,Facid kept in a bottle of hair dye.
OL,16,FHis victim has undergone numerous
OL,17,Ftreatments and procedures since the
OL,18,Fattack.
