OL,3,CMan jailed after throwing acid in a
OL,4,Cteenager's face
OL,6,FMartins had pleaded guilty to robbery,
OL,7,Fpossession of a corrosive substance
OL,8,Fand witness intimidation.
OL,10,FHe was sentenced to eight years and
OL,11,Ftwo months at Minshull Street Crown
OL,12,FCourt in Manchester on Tuesday. The
OL,13,Fsentence also included unrelated drugs
OL,14,Foffences from 2022.
OL,16,FDetective Constable Heather Parke,
OL,17,Ffrom GMP's Stockport district, said:
OL,18,F"The effects of attacks involving
OL,19,Fcorrosive substances are well-known,
OL,20,Fand can result in severe, life-
OL,21,Fchanging injuries or even death.
