OL,6,F"Using them in attacks is utterly vile
OL,7,Fand I am glad Martins is now behind
OL,8,Fbars for his vicious assault. His
OL,9,Fvictim received injuries from which he
OL,10,Fis still suffering, and has already
OL,11,Freceived numerous treatments.
OL,13,F"We have zero tolerance for these sort
OL,14,Fof crimes, and we put considerable
OL,15,Fresources into ensuring that Martins
OL,16,Fwas arrested, charged, and sentenced.
OL,17,FHe now has a long time to think about
OL,18,Fhis actions inside a prison cell."
